Fortnite – Round 24
05 Nov 2019, 14:11 by Alberto Desfassiaux
Así es, estamos de vuelta. No tenemos pensado dejar que Fortnite nos derrote y hasta que no consigamos ganar al menos una partida, seguiremos intentando. Desafortunadamente, en esta ocasión nos tocó fallar de nueva cuenta… pero estuvo divertido.

Fortnite - Round 24
05 Nov 2019, 14:11 by Alberto Desfassiaux
That's right, we are back. We do not plan to let Fortnite defeat us and until we can win at least one game, we will keep trying. Unfortunately, this time we had to fail again ... but it was fun.
